'''中美国'''（{{lang|en|Chimerica}}），又译'''中美联合体'''、'''中美经济联合体'''、'''中美共同体'''、'''中华美利坚'''等，是[[尼尔·弗格森|尼尔·弗格森]]和莫里茨·苏拉里克创造的[[英语|英语]]新词“Chimerica”的[[意译|意译]]，指[[中华人民共和国|中国]]和[[美国|美国]]间的互利互依关系，与[[希腊神话|希腊神话]]中会喷火的怪物[[喀邁拉|喀邁拉]]（{{lang|en|Chimera}}）的拼写相近<ref>{{cite web |url=http://jfki.fu-berlin.de/faculty/economics/team/persons/schularick/chimerica.pdf |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2009-08-18 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100613083353/http://www.jfki.fu-berlin.de/faculty/economics/team/persons/schularick/Chimerica.pdf |archivedate=2010-06-13 }}</ref><ref>http://www.ft.com/cms/s/0/c7804616-d3b7-11dd-989e-000077b07658,Authorised=true.html?_i_location=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ft.com%2Fcms%2Fs%2F0%2Fc7804616-d3b7-11dd-989e-000077b07658.html&_i_referer=http%3A%2F%2Fsearch.ft.com%2Fsearch%3FqueryText%3DChimerica%26x%3D11%26y%3D5%26aje%3Dtrue%26dse%3D%26dsz%3D&nclick_check=1{{dead link|date=2018年5月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2008/11/16/AR2008111601736.html | work=The Washington Post | first=Niall | last=Ferguson | title=Team 'Chimerica' | date=2008-11-17 | accessdate=2011-08-17 | archive-date=2011-01-20 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110120192950/http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2008/11/16/AR2008111601736.html | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/nathan-gardels/niall-ferguson-is-us-chin_b_245470.html |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2011-08-17 |archive-date=2012-01-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120129052700/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/nathan-gardels/niall-ferguson-is-us-chin_b_245470.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。本词最早在2006年底提出。

